    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Dogs are a huge theme in the Transkei. Damo is a border collie. Fred a Great Dane. And I a golden retriever. We start the run. Pull into a spaza shop for a lunch bar and coke. We take a few wrong turns. “Fastpacking - where the fuck are we?” Fred. ",
            "link": null
          },
